high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffeetable in the living room.
Take the butterknife from the table.
Turn around and go near the eggplant table.
Cut the eggplant into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the butterknife into the fridge.
Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the eggplant from the table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the eggplant into the refrigerator.
Then take it out and go near the coffeetable in the living room.
Put the eggplant on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Eggplant on the CoffeeTable in the living room.

high_descs: Go straight into the room ahead, then turn right and go to the wall, then right again into the large room, approaching the coffee table in front of the TV ahead.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Go to the white dining table against the wall next to the fridge to the left of the TV.
Slice the eggplant on the table.
Turn to the fridge next to the table.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn back to the table you sliced the eggplant on.
Pick up a slice of the eggplant.
Go back to the fridge.
Cool the eggplant in the fridge and pick it back up.
Go back to the coffee table you got the knife from.
Put the eggplant down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice an eggplant, refrigerate a slice and place it on a coffee table.

high_descs: Go ahead straight to the wall, then turn right and go straight ot the wall again, then right into the larger room, going ahead towards the sitting area in front of the TV, approaching the brown coffeetable.
Pick up the butterknife from the coffee table.
Go towards the eggplant table towards the other end of this large room.
Cut the eggplant on the table.
Go to the fridge right next to the white table.
Place the butterknife inside the fridge.
Return to the diningtable.
Pick up one half of the eggplant.
Go back to the fridge.
Put the eggplant in the fridge, let it cool, then retrieve it.
Return to the brown coffeetable you got the knife from.
Place the eggplant down on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Cut an Eggplant in half, cool half of that in a fridge, and place that half on a CoffeeTable.
